Drawing map

# dev.off()
mapCountryData(myMap
               , nameColumnToPlot="matleave_13"
               , catMethod = "categorical"
)

Drawing map by specific colors

# self-defined colors
colors <- c("#FF8000", "#A9D0F5", "#58ACFA", "#0080FF", "#084B8A")
mapCountryData(myMap
               , nameColumnToPlot="matleave_13"
               , catMethod = "categorical"
               , colourPalette = colors
               , addLegend="FALSE"
)
